OL,4,CCovid: Delay to full reopening a hammer
OL,5,Cblow, says live event sector
OL,6, Live music, theatre and other events
OL,7, have been dealt a "hammer blow" by a
OL,8, four-week delay to the final stage of
OL,9, easing lockdown restrictions in
OL,10, England, industry figures have said.
OL,12,FThe move means the capacity of venues
OL,13,Fwill remain limited by the requirements
OL,14,Faround social distancing.
OL,16,FThe entertainment sector has appealed
OL,17,Ffor urgent financial support.
OL,19,FThe Society of London Theatre said the
OL,20,Fdecision would "have serious
OL,21,Fimplications for many theatres".
